   &UR; BUSINESS DAY _ (Moved in ``f'' category)  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CHASE-INVEST (New York) _ Is Chase Manhattan Bank ready,
finally, to join the big leagues of investment banking? By Laura M.
Holson.
</P>
