<HEADLINE>
MUGABE: HERO TURNED DESPOT AND NOW, FIGURE OF RIDICULE  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Analysis...ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 575-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
