<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLASS-COLUMN-$ADV02-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: GATES HITS THE E-BOOK CIRCUITS
 &HT;    Moving in the (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, July 2.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
