</P>
<P>
   CABBAGE-SALAD (Undated) _ It is a tight affiliation with picnics
and cookouts for a salad of shredded raw cabbage to wedge its way
into a summer menu. Yet if there is any fault with coleslaw,
fingers must point to all too often a heavy ladling of mayonnaise
or a lack of discretion with the vinegar. By MARYELLEN DRISCOLL.
</P>
