all some big favors. The court rejected appeals by Elin Gonzlez's
Miami relatives and sent that over-publicized little boy home _
right, it's his home, as unbearable as the Leninist landlord is. By
ROB MORSE.
</P>
<P>
   INTERSTATE-HIGHWAYS (Danville, Calif.) _ The history of the
Interstate Highway System illustrates how democratically elected
governments often operate. And as with other issues when
politicians try to please voters, government took a short-term view
with the highway program and the future took a back seat to the
present. By CYNTHIA BASS.
</P>
<P>
   HARRY-POTTER (San Francisco) _ Harry Potter has given children a
gift: magic and excitement that don't require the flip of a switch
or the bleep of a modem. So I say we return Harry's gift. Ignore
the toys that manufacturers will cash in on to take advantage of
Harry's popularity. Stay out of the movie theaters ``Harry Potter''
hits the silver screen. And head to the library when Harry Potter
IV arrives. By LYSSA FRIEDMAN.
