<HEADLINE>
SPECTATOR SPORTS  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of ``HIGH STYLE AND MORE.''
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 (Three color slides are available.) 
 From WWD 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    Michael Kors is playing both sides of the net for resort. The
designer is volleying between ladylike looks with a hint of the
preppy for Collection, while for his bridge line, Kors, he's going
the super-sporty route. Both, however, still have a sexy edge.
 c.2000 Fairchild Publications 
