<P>
   MEXICO-ELECTION _ MEXICO CITY _ An advance story that will
profile Mexico as a country _ contradictions, poverty levels,
educational snapshot, its standing in the world as a major economy
or Third World wannabe _ and sum up what has emerged as core issues
