<DOCNO> NYT20000629.0240 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-29 16:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8512 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-ANTIQUES-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      06-29 1185
