<DOCNO> NYT20000629.0335 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-29 20:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8709 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2N     06-29 0657
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-2NDLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
