a non-toxic compound that can produce dramatic weight loss without
any side effects. So far, only mice have benefited from the
discovery of C75. By Megan Scott 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   LAND-AND-HOLD (Boston) _ Flights at Logan International Airport
have been encountering long delays, not because of weather or
antiquated air-traffic control equipment, but because pilots are
refusing to practice ``land and hold'' at intersecting runways. By
Matthew Brelis. 1000 words.
