in every respect except one: It lacks the original's brevity. While
the Rocky and Bullwinkle segments were only five or 10 minutes of a
half-hour show, this movie goes on for 88 minutes. Its first act is
delightful, but it just doesn't have the juice to sustain a feature
length and finally becomes redundant and tiresome.
