<SLUG> BC-ROCKER-SCENE0630-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Rocker, Mets fans behave on first day
 &HT;    By Jill Vejnoska
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
